					<img src="images/misc/quote_icon.png" alt="Quote" /> Originally Posted by <strong>angelatc</strong>
					<a href="showthread.php?s=2eaadabea0798c9b320975dbcfee538c&amp;p=4994982#post4994982" rel="nofollow"><img class="inlineimg" src="images/buttons/viewpost-right.png" alt="View Post" /></a>
